---
title: Chicken Shawarma with Bulgur and Green Bean Tabbouleh
description: André is a huge fan of our shawarma seasoning, and it's no surprise, it's delicious! He used to add it to so many recipes that he had to be banned from using it for a while, but luckily for you, the ban has been lifted! André's seasoned some juicy chicken mini fillets here, it's a speedy winner!
